==俄屬北美==

[[File:Russian_claims_in_the_americas_19th_century.png|150px]]
1799年，[[俄羅斯帝國|俄羅斯帝國]][[皇帝#俄罗斯|皇帝]][[保羅一世|保羅一世]]發布[[政令_(俄羅斯)|政令]]，建立[[俄美公司|俄美公司]]。該特許公司被授予壟斷控制今[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]{{le|北緯55度線|55th parallel north}}以北的地區。它還被授予往南方佔領的權利，只要南方的土地還沒被佔據或尚未隸屬於其他國家。<ref>{{cite book |author= United States, Bering Sea Tribunal of Arbitration |title= Fur-seal Arbitration: The Case of the United States before the Tribunal of Arbitration to convene at Paris under the provisions of the treaty between the United States of America and Great Britain, concluded February 29, 1892 |year= 1892 |publisher= [[美國政府出版局|美國政府出版局]] |oclc= 68198841 |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=LYoGAAAAMAAJ |page= 14 |access-date= 2016-07-16 |archive-date= 2016-05-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160507210533/https://books.google.com/books?id=LYoGAAAAMAAJ |dead-url= no }}</ref>1821年，俄美公司更新特許證，同年9月俄羅斯發布政令，宣告俄羅斯的主權範圍向南擴張至北緯45度50分線，該緯線以北水域禁止外國船隻駛入。剛開始因為美國和英國的抗議，到1822年修改為北緯51度線。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nosracines.ca/page.aspx?id=321408&qryID=d8121004-8d7a-4f2d-b8bb-ef07a8eed9d0|2=|title=Review of the Alaska Boundary Question|last=Begg|first=Alexander|agency=nosracines.ca|publisher=Unknown|year=1900|pages=1–2|access-date=12 December 2014}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>隨後的談判及{{le|俄美1824年條約|Russo-American Treaty of 1824}}、{{le|聖彼得堡條約 (1825年)|Treaty of Saint Petersburg (1825)|聖彼得堡條約}}清楚的確立了[[俄屬北美|俄屬北美]]的永久南界：{{le|北緯54度40分線|Parallel 54°40′ north}}。<ref>{{cite book |last= Haycox |first= Stephen W. |title= Alaska: An American Colony |year= 2002 |publisher= University of Washington Press |isbn= 978-0-295-98249-6 |pages= 1118–1122 |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=8yu3pYpzLdUC |access-date= 2016-07-16 |archive-date= 2016-05-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160517163632/https://books.google.com/books?id=8yu3pYpzLdUC |dead-url= no }}</ref>

